      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Global relative hemolysis index validation against FDA GCBP experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at five operating points (2\u20136 L/min, 2000\u20133500 RPM). Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed at all operating points. Agreement within 12% across all cases.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/uq-001-global-hemolysis-gci-interval"
    },
    {
