      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Shear stress distribution validation at worst-case operating condition",
      "description": "Volume-averaged and peak shear stress distributions compared between CFD predictions and particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements at the worst-case operating point (4 L/min, 3000 RPM). Spatial agreement assessed via area-weighted error metric. Inherent variability in PIV ensemble measurements assessed qualitatively by the analyst based on observed spread across repeated acquisitions; no structured probabilistic characterization of aleatory uncertainty was performed or linked.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/uq-002-shear-stress-epistemic-mesh"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vr-003-pressure-head-validation",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Pump pressure-head curve validation across operating envelope",
